Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼從什麼開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也考慮了很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得首先從唯開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在大食堂的遊擊Live裡擔任樂隊主唱的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一直很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還一直以欺負日向為樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在樂隊裡當主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為她應該相當滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後只差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為從背後再推她一把就能夠離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼想的話就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你那裡的整備如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然要費點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hand sonic version V
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是Hand sonic version V
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起天使還更像是惡魔用的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你說是冷酷的天使所以才做成這樣讓人不舒服的樣子...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 很好啊  真的讓人非常討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 非常好 非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後再弄上翅膀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翅膀？ 弄上之後要幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 看起來很酷不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那樣比較像天使嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我該怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼辦 你在她們正在練習的時候出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從其他的社團都投訴你們發出的噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後指著唯這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是你的吉他彈得太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的關係樂隊都廢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此暫時沒收吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後搶走唯的吉他離開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然唯會追出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一直逃到中庭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡我會假裝撞到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時你扔掉吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接住後 你就那樣逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就能和她兩個人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那麼先去練習的地方開始找機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.49,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}革命を起こしにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.49,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}去發起革命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.46,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}夢を叶えていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.46,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}去實現夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.67,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}駆け出したらどこまでもいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.67,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}只要出發就能到達任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.22,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}アインシュタイン。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.22,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,愛因斯坦...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 唯 不要繼續那種忽快忽慢的節奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯 唱和彈專攻一個比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣下去太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 岩澤前輩可以邊彈邊唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為岩澤兩個都厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在努力的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家說得太嚴厲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Live不是依然很火熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這次是新曲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的吉他彈得太爛了 整個樂隊都廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬就看穿了現在的樂隊的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她懂音樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會  我還以為大家都察覺不到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此暫時要沒收這個吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她沒追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 不彈吉他節奏就不亂了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是音色太單調了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是需要節奏吉他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再多加一個節奏吉他手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 唔 我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主唱必須要同時擔任吉他手的畫面才是最酷的 明白嗎喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇這傢伙對久子前輩發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去把吉他拿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額  麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 唯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊在這裡  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 扔太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前輩幫我從天使那保護的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那傢伙跑哪去了啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的什麼喂啊 你還依然為所欲為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 為所欲為  我才沒有為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是成為了樂隊主唱麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還彈吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有呢 這只是想做的事情其中之一而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 還有其他想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊 很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說很多 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 其他想做的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想說的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 說給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要做的事情比一般人要多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道為什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 活著的時候沒能做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯 就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候 被車子從背後撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 身體就不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能整天躺在床上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人看護就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能完全依靠母親照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直覺得非常對不起母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看電視的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:08:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到音樂節目里樂隊表演時覺得如果自己能變成這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還有什麼想做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 棒球直播  也經常看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球的話棒球大賽的時候不是打過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我不是沒打嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安打？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒打到就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我在想在樂隊那邊變得更純熟之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就開始練習棒球了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩方面都要練習很棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先都說給我聽聽吧 其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是曾經很火熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可能確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣太廣泛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼世界有同時搞樂隊棒球和足球的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會還有其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙 哪個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 全部憧憬的都是從電視裡看來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這真是難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把剛才聽到的全部都實現什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我來讓你實現那些夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先從簡單的地方開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從職業摔跤開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業摔跤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德式拱橋摔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種華麗的招怎麼做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找一個簡單的關節技之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我一直很想來一次 德式拱橋摔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且之後直接一招取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別一臉天真地說這種可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比看上去力氣大很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這行得通！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我一個女孩子是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就差一點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可惜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再來一次行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先找個草地行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 怎麼會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 真的不是笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起下次一定會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是最後了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 其實不會做拱橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做來看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然原因是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這個害我白白N次失去意識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是拱橋的特訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話給我幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 給我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人家從來沒這樣過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不會這個就成不了德式拱橋摔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全身都在哆嗦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 沒所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雙手都緊鎖住身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣掙脫不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美了 太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德式拱橋摔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 成功了 我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的還要持續多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個就足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一對一的PK行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要 人家要運球連過5人的射門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬拉多納哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 明白了 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 TK 知道松下五段在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那傢伙不能像我一樣跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't let me cry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的...那麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行 in the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山裡修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和跳舞完全無關的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時不會回來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Waoh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來能把我提到的成員帶來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}教學樓 C棟 男子便所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事要對由莉保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從天使那裡收到了這樣的信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連一介女流之輩也無法取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男人令旁人都覺得羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你居然能看懂令旁人都覺得羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的笨蛋治好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 連笨蛋也能讀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如依靠運動精神地糾正你們那種娘娘腔的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後在足球場上等你們 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人莫名其妙的內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是她寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的天使已經不是之前的天使了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許多東西都混在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以連這種笨蛋一樣的挑戰書也寫得出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種蠢事誰會幹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向由莉貝彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說了 要對由莉保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果對由莉說了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定又會發展成激烈的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上面寫著要靠運動精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是想要通過體育來正大光明的一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那是對我們男生的挑戰書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果告訴了給由莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才有損我們的名譽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就以這五人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiss you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等你這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}足球場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是唯啊 那傢伙在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始踢球了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 寫信的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是對平時不中用的我們看不順眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才做出了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 一定不能讓他進球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場比賽不能輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們男人會獲勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 守門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開 你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 這麼爛的帶球技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破綻百出 覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 超了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼野田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁判 剛才那個該紅牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在裝誰啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 TK 音無
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Easy come easy go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪邊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 最後是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了你也要進球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的體育精神哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踢吧 必殺斷頭殺人射門！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是想殺我還是想進球充滿吐槽點的射門過來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 啊 進了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進了 進了 連過5人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們居然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是唯一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scamble it tremble down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 雖然被截斷了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有晃過守門員踢 全是亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要飛多遠才算本壘打？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然是飛到網後面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 盡力揮棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是中了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再仔細看好球 用球棒的中間擊打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的觸球點太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉著眼怎麼可能會中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 無能為力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不行了吧 累了所以握力也開始下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就算訓練下去也沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你喊得再大聲 擊球聲還是這麼輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還早呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！好可惜...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天已經黑了 連球都看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒...啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也來嗎？來打真的棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振臂高揮(Full swing)嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都沒打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾打打或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 一點都沒打到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出來給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就說了給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎做都是不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒所謂了 這夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你的關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣幫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油到最後吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全壘打什麼的 就像開玩笑一樣的夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算打不出本壘打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體能活動這麼久 已經足夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都像在參加社團活動一樣 真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說過的吧 因為我以前根本不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 全部都實現了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身體不能動的時候想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 還有一個呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子最崇高的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我既不能做家事也不能洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此 一個人的話 什麼也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會要這種包袱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神真是過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的幸福全部都奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回...事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 前輩能和我結婚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 前輩又不瞭解真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實中 曾經活著的你是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會跟你結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你身上有什麼障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小唯不能走路也站不起來的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說無論什麼障礙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能走路 站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算生不了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我也要和你結婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直都會留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡遇見的你不是虛假的唯 是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在哪裡遇見你 我一定都會喜歡上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能以那六十億分之一的機率遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那時候你身子還是動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和你結婚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇見不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小唯一直在家臥床不起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是打棒球的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定有天我會不小心打破你家的玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後去撿球的時候 見到你在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 那就是相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭話之後 發現很合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺就天天見面了 也開始護理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這發展如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...吶 在那時要讓總是一個人努力照顧我的媽媽輕鬆一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之後打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會奉陪到最後的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.57,0:24:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟還有很讓人操心的傢伙們在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.77,0:26:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才究竟砍了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.20,0:26:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.37,0:26:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,描述得詳細一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.18,0:26:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能以影去形容
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.46,0:26:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛趕到的野田打倒了那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.85,0:26:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山一個人差點遇險
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.42,0:26:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇險...是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.46,0:26:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}這世界開始產生變異了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}你又做了什麼好事啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}他居然會摘下眼鏡...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.46,0:26:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}這是惡夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}我原本也打算幫忙的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}我不需要幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}有東西進來了，音無！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.14,0:26:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}這也太不尋常了...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.21,0:26:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}Dancing in the shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.58,0:26:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}被天使消去還比較好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.69,0:26:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}會消失的！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.67,0:26:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.53,0:26:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}該死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.23,0:26:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}由莉貝！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.49,0:26:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(1000,20)}{\fad(20,1000)}我會等的！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.18,0:26:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(20,2000)}{\fad(2000,20)}那麼，有緣再見。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:13.24,*IN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:40.94,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}顔を合わすたび ケンカした二人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:40.94,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}只要照面就會拌嘴的二人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:47.03,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}それもいい思い出だった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:47.03,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}同樣也是美好的回億
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:55.68,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}君が教えてくれたんだ もう恐くない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:55.68,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是你教會我這些 讓我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:03.74,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}どんな不自由でも 幸せは掴める
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:03.74,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無論怎樣不自由 也能夠抓住幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:08.49,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:08.49,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}因此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:19.61,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ひとりでもゆくよ たとえつらくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:19.61,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一個人也要前行 即使艱難無比
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:27.54,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}君と見た夢は必ず持っていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:27.54,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一定會將和你共同夢想一起帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:35.82,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}君とがよかった 他の誰でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:35.82,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}慶幸曾經不是別人而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:39.49,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}でもねダメだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:39.49,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是吶 不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:43.72,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}君はいないんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:43.72,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:08.57,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ずっと遊んでいる そんな気がしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:08.57,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}似乎只是一直在玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:14.73,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}気がしていただけ 分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:14.73,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}稍微注意一下就能發現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:23.68,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生まれてきたこと もう後悔はしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:23.68,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對出生於世上再也不覺得後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:31.65,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}祭りの後みたい 寂しいけどそろそろ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:31.65,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}彷彿節日過後 儘管寂寞也差不多該
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:36.39,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:36.39,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:47.56,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}どこまでもゆくよ ここで知ったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:47.56,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}無論哪裡都能去 在這裡了解的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:55.55,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}幸せという夢を叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:55.55,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}要將所有幸福的夢實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:03.69,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}君と離れても どんなに遠くなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:03.69,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}即使與你分離 無論相隔多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:11.61,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}新しい朝にあたしは生きるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:11.61,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}向著新的早晨而活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:19.45,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}巡って流れて時は移ろいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:19.45,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}循環流逝時間更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:27.56,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}もうなにがあったか思い出せないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.67,0:24:27.56,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}即使已經想不起曾經存在的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:35.64,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}目を閉じてみれば誰かの笑い声
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:35.64,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}閉上眼睛卻傳來不知誰的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.77,0:24:44.14,*IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}なぜかそれが今 一番の宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.77,0:24:44.14,*IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是如今最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:13.24,*IN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:25.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}目覚めては繰り返す眠い朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:32.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}襟の帯を着付く締め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}教室のドア潜ると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:45.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}ほんの少し胸を張って歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:52.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}そんな日常に吹き抜ける風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:56.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}聞こえた気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:02.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}感じた気がしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}震え出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:09.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今この胸で潜る気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:14.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}幾億の星が 消え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}去ってくのを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:20.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}見送った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}手を振った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:28.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}良かったねと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:25.81,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}不斷醒來昏昏入睡的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:32.41,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}仔細穿戴好衣襟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.29,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要穿過教室的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:45.97,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就會略微挺起胸 邁步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:52.78,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}穿過那樣日常的清風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:56.50,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我似乎能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:02.34,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}似乎已經感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.05,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}開始顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:09.67,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}似乎正潛入胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:14.25,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}幾億的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.65,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:20.55,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我目送著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.93,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}揮起了手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:28.23,OP-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}說著 太好了呢
